  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      300 recurrent implantation failure patients will be alternatively assigned to assisted
      hatching , endometrial scratch , and no treatment ,100 patients in each group
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Group 1 consists of 100 patients will undergo endometrial scratch followed by controlled
      ovarian hyperstimulation Group 2 consists of 100 patients will undergo controlled ovarian
      hyperstimulation&amp; assisted hatching Group 3 consists of 100 patients will undergo controlled
      ovarian hyperstimulation
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
